This is the doctor.

42:32.750 --> 42:33.940
Easy.

42:46.060 --> 42:48.290
Easy, easy. Easy! Easy!

42:48.390 --> 42:49.760
I can't, I can't.

42:52.160 --> 42:53.630
Tell him, easy.

42:53.730 --> 42:55.760
The bullet didn't
touch her spine.

