43:05.640 --> 43:07.640
Don't you fucking lie to me.
You tell me what he said.

43:07.750 --> 43:09.580
Tell me what he said!

43:11.220 --> 43:13.120
Hospital. Hospital.

43:13.220 --> 43:14.520
I know, hospital! What can you do?

43:14.620 --> 43:16.380
