- Richard.

43:49.920 --> 43:50.910
No, no, no, Richard.

43:51.020 --> 43:53.120
We have to
hold her down.

43:53.230 --> 43:56.680
- Richard. Richard. No, no, no, no.
- Wait. Wait. Wait. Wait.

44:03.000 --> 44:05.990
- Richard, don't let him.
- Honey, we have to do this.

44:06.970 --> 44:09.670
It's still bleeding. We got to stop
the bleeding. You gotta do this.

44:09.780 --> 44:11.300
- We have to do this.
