44:11.410 --> 44:12.540
- Listen to me.
- No, no, no, please.

44:12.650 --> 44:14.770
No, no, no, no. Richard, don't.

44:16.480 --> 44:18.110
- No!
- You got to be still.

44:18.220 --> 44:21.310
- Richard, don't let him! No.
- You got to be still.

44:22.090 --> 44:24.060
Be strong, be strong.

44:51.480 --> 44:53.110
