48:14.620 --> 48:16.020
<i>I left you a bento box. Papa.</i>

48:21.830 --> 48:25.820
<i>I'm on my way to your place.</i>

48:26.600 --> 48:28.430
Where are you?

48:31.600 --> 48:33.130
