to ask my dad about the same things.

49:33.430 --> 49:35.300
They're just not convinced,
are they?

49:42.370 --> 49:45.540
Believe it or not,
I liked one of the cops.

49:47.280 --> 49:48.270
Idiot.

49:48.910 --> 49:50.850
Did you put on some panties?

50:54.110 --> 50:55.700
