it was here?

50:56.250 --> 50:58.610
An American stopped me.

50:58.750 --> 51:03.050
I was scared.
He was covered in blood.

51:04.660 --> 51:05.990
Where was the bus stopped?

51:06.090 --> 51:07.220
Over there.

51:08.030 --> 51:10.360
<i>Captain Alarid... Captain Alarid.</i>

51:11.660 --> 51:12.650
<i>I found cartridges.</i>

51:18.970 --> 51:21.840
We found four.
Here's one.

51:29.950 --> 51:31.070
Did you search all over?

51:31.420 --> 51:32.610
Yes, the whole mountain.

51:52.100 --> 51:53.300
They're from around here.

51:54.570 --> 51:56.630
