- Drop your weapon.

52:26.570 --> 52:27.600
I don't have a weapon.

52:27.710 --> 52:28.700
Drop it now.

52:28.810 --> 52:29.900
I told you to drop
your weapon.

52:30.010 --> 52:31.100
This is just my knife.

52:32.280 --> 52:33.240
Get on the ground.

52:33.350 --> 52:34.330
What did we do?

52:34.450 --> 52:35.780
Get down on the ground...
face down.

52:38.420 --> 52:39.480
Don't look at me.

52:40.590 --> 52:41.880
What did we do?

52:47.490 --> 52:50.690
Take these skins to Najib,
see if he wants to buy them.

53:08.080 --> 53:09.710
Why did you shoot at the bus?

53:13.550 --> 53:15.780
