53:17.060 --> 53:18.180
Then who?

53:25.460 --> 53:27.160
It wasn't me.

53:31.500 --> 53:33.300
That was your rifle.

53:37.380 --> 53:39.280
I sold it yesterday.

53:40.280 --> 53:41.680
Who did you sell it to?

54:11.380 --> 54:13.870
Do you know where
Abdullah Adboum lives?

54:15.180 --> 54:16.670
Yes.

54:16.920 --> 54:19.180
You have to go over those mountains.

54:23.990 --> 54:25.550
Who lives
in this area?

54:25.660 --> 54:28.990
We live here with our mother.
Abdullah lives on the other side.

54:32.700 --> 54:37.900
If you're lying, I'm going to
come back and cut your balls off.

54:38.000 --> 54:40.270
You can come back
anytime you like.

54:49.380 --> 54:51.370
Don't walk
between the graves.

55:14.110 --> 55:15.630
Papa... Papa...

55:15.740 --> 55:16.760
What happened?

55:16.910 --> 55:19.000
