they're looking for you.

55:19.110 --> 55:20.310
Me? Why?

55:20.580 --> 55:22.950
No, not for you...
they're looking for us.

55:23.080 --> 55:24.410
Looking for you?
Why?

55:25.220 --> 55:26.950
Because of the tourist.

55:27.450 --> 55:28.510
What tourist?

55:28.650 --> 55:30.420
The American...
Yussef killed her.

55:30.590 --> 55:31.650
Liar, we both did.

55:31.990 --> 55:33.150
What are you saying?

55:33.360 --> 55:35.190
Yussef started shooting
at the cars...

55:35.560 --> 55:37.030
because Hassan said
that the bullet could go far.

55:37.130 --> 55:38.960
Liar, you started shooting at the cars.

55:39.100 --> 55:40.120
But you killed her.

55:40.230 --> 55:41.600
What are you saying?

55:41.700 --> 55:44.530
Yussef killed the American
and he spies on Zohra naked...

55:44.640 --> 55:46.430
and Zohra lets him watch her.

55:46.770 --> 55:47.930
That's garbage.

55:48.270 --> 55:51.540
It's not garbage.
She's a street girl and he spies on her.

55:59.180 --> 56:01.310
Time to drink!

56:28.650 --> 56:33.110
This song is dedicated
from Luis to Patricia...

56:33.220 --> 56:35.190
the most beautiful bride
in the world.

57:08.920 --> 57:13.860
I think Aunt Amelia has to dance.

58:02.470 --> 58:05.030
Amelia, can I have this dance?

58:05.940 --> 58:08.210
I don't think your wife
would like that.

58:08.310 --> 58:13.050
Ohh, she passed away 10 years ago.
Come on Amelia.

1:00:59.520 --> 1:01:03.110
Let's go dance... You have
something white on your face.

1:01:03.220 --> 1:01:05.450
Don't get excited,
it's only cake.

