1:04:11.140 --> 1:04:13.610
Oh, fuck that. Come on.

1:04:15.910 --> 1:04:17.210
Fuck you.

1:04:22.790 --> 1:04:24.080
Tom, where are you going?

1:04:24.190 --> 1:04:26.990
Get back. Wait there. Get back.

1:04:32.460 --> 1:04:34.860
- Look, we're leaving.
