- Well, let him come, then.

1:04:45.240 --> 1:04:46.940
His wife's in no condition to travel.

1:04:47.050 --> 1:04:48.770
There's people in no condition
to be kept waiting.

1:04:48.880 --> 1:04:50.010
Can't you see that?

1:04:50.110 --> 1:04:53.450
Please wait. The ambulance
is gonna be here any minute, right?

1:04:53.550 --> 1:04:55.180
It's gonna be here any minute.

1:04:55.290 --> 1:04:57.810
So I'm asking you all to please wait.

1:05:01.190 --> 1:05:04.360
Thirty minutes.
We're giving you thirty minutes.

1:05:45.740 --> 1:05:47.070
Who are they?

1:05:48.110 --> 1:05:49.440
My cousins.

1:05:49.540 --> 1:05:50.940
