1:05:59.250 --> 1:06:01.120
What is your name?

1:06:10.430 --> 1:06:11.860
Chieko.

1:06:12.770 --> 1:06:15.530
My name's Haruki.

1:06:32.650 --> 1:06:34.710
It's whisky.

1:06:49.800 --> 1:06:53.100
