1:09:31.570 --> 1:09:33.040
You smell good.

1:14:34.350 --> 1:14:36.940
Welcome home... may I help you?

1:14:47.300 --> 1:14:51.030
Are you sure
you want him to come now?

1:15:06.680 --> 1:15:09.380
