1:16:44.080 --> 1:16:45.180
Go get it.

1:17:09.580 --> 1:17:13.910
He's holding the rifle
he gave me.

1:17:39.840 --> 1:17:41.270
We're going to Najib's house.

1:17:41.410 --> 1:17:44.470
If the cops come,
tell them we went south.

1:18:03.070 --> 1:18:05.530
This Abdullah doesn't live
in the area you told us.

1:18:05.670 --> 1:18:06.660
Are you playing with us?

1:18:07.900 --> 1:18:10.130
He lives in the area
he told you.

1:18:10.240 --> 1:18:12.230
He lives there?

1:18:12.710 --> 1:18:15.180
You're going to take us.

1:18:54.320 --> 1:18:55.950
