1:24:25.630 --> 1:24:27.060
Close it up.

1:24:30.370 --> 1:24:32.100
Get back in the vehicle.

1:24:34.910 --> 1:24:36.870
Glove compartment, ma'am.

1:24:43.980 --> 1:24:45.310
Purse?

1:25:08.540 --> 1:25:09.740
All right.

1:25:14.850 --> 1:25:18.580
