<i>to the principal's office
'cause she was really crying.</i>

2:09:08.180 --> 2:09:13.420
Mr. Wataya, this officer
has been looking for you.

2:09:17.060 --> 2:09:21.460
Good evening, I'm Lieutenant Mamiya.

2:09:22.470 --> 2:09:24.660
Good evening, how can I help you?

2:09:27.300 --> 2:09:30.140
Sir, there was an incident and...

2:09:31.340 --> 2:09:33.240
I'm sorry to bother you, but...

2:09:33.410 --> 2:09:37.070
do you own a .270 caliber
Winchester M70 rifle?

2:09:38.450 --> 2:09:40.250
Registration number...

2:09:42.790 --> 2:09:45.190
UK-9023.

2:09:45.990 --> 2:09:49.480
I don't remember the number,
but I did have a rifle like that.

2:09:50.290 --> 2:09:53.130
Is it true that you gave that rifle
to a Mr. Hassan Ibrahim...

2:09:53.260 --> 2:09:54.890
who lives in Morocco?

2:09:55.200 --> 2:09:56.220
Hassan Ibrahim?

2:09:58.140 --> 2:10:00.800
He says he was
your guide in a hunt.

2:10:01.070 --> 2:10:03.100
Hassan? Yes,
I remember him well.

2:10:03.210 --> 2:10:08.870
He was a good guide and a very
good man, I gave him the rifle in thanks.

2:10:11.080 --> 2:10:12.550
Did anything happen?

2:10:13.750 --> 2:10:16.950
That rifle was used
in an attempted murder...

2:10:17.060 --> 2:10:21.120
and the Moroccan police want
to confirm it's not off the black market.

2:10:21.230 --> 2:10:23.790
No, I gave it to him.

2:10:25.660 --> 2:10:28.160
Is Hassan OK?

2:10:29.640 --> 2:10:31.430
I don't know about that.

2:10:35.910 --> 2:10:38.070
Am I legally involved?

2:10:38.440 --> 2:10:43.540
Not for the moment, but can you
come down to the station tomorrow?

2:10:43.780 --> 2:10:45.410
I have a few questions.

2:10:47.620 --> 2:10:48.640
Can I leave now?

2:10:49.920 --> 2:10:51.410
Good night.

2:10:55.600 --> 2:10:56.720
Excuse me.

2:10:58.730 --> 2:11:03.640
I heard from your daughter...
about your wife on the balcony.

2:11:04.810 --> 2:11:06.170
I'm very sorry.

2:11:07.040 --> 2:11:08.410
What balcony?

2:11:10.310 --> 2:11:14.250
About how your wife killed herself
by jumping off the balcony.

2:11:22.190 --> 2:11:26.790
My wife never jumped off a balcony.
She shot herself in the head.

2:11:26.900 --> 2:11:29.090
My daughter was the first to find her.

2:11:31.130 --> 2:11:33.790
I've explained it
to the police many times.

2:11:35.640 --> 2:11:38.110
Don't bother us with that anymore.

2:11:39.240 --> 2:11:41.870
I'm very sorry sir, we won't
bother you anymore.

2:11:42.280 --> 2:11:43.470
Good night.

2:12:36.070 --> 2:12:37.660
Another shochu.

2:13:15.970 --> 2:13:19.030
<i>Susan Jones, who was wounded
in a terrorist attack in Morocco...</i>

2:13:19.140 --> 2:13:23.080
<i>was discharged from a Casablanca
hospital this morning, local time.</i>

2:13:23.250 --> 2:13:27.020
<i>The American people finally have
a happy ending, after five days...</i>

2:13:27.120 --> 2:13:30.390
<i>of frantic phone calls
and hand wringing.</i>

